    "Similarly, on the SQuAD dev dataset, our proposed method excelled with precision, recall, and F1-Score reaching 82.8%, 87.0%, and 84.8%, while other QA applications reported lower scores of 80.4%, 86.3%, and 83.2%, respectively.",
    "These results underscore the superior performance of our proposed method across both datasets that can be visualized in Fig. 10.",
